對任意正五角錐而言，其側面邊長<math>e</math>與斜高<math>s</math>可透過底面邊長<math>a</math>與高<math>h</math>來決定：<ref name="mw"/>
:<math>e = \sqrt{h^2+\frac{5+\sqrt{5}}{10}a^2} \approx \sqrt{0.7236 a^2 + h^2}</math><ref name="mw"/>
:<math>s = \sqrt{h^2+\frac{5+2\sqrt{5}}{20}a^2} \approx \sqrt{0.4736 a^2 + h^2}</math><ref name="mw"/>
此時這個高為<math>h</math>且底面邊長為<math>a</math>的正五角錐[[表面積|表面積]]<math>A</math>與[[體積|體積]]<math>V</math>為：<ref name="mw"/>
:<math>S = \frac{5a\left(a+\sqrt{a^2+4\left(5-2\sqrt{5}\right) h^2}\right)}{4\sqrt{5-2\sqrt{5}}}</math><ref name="mw"/>
:<math>V = \frac{a^2h\sqrt{25+10\sqrt{5}}}{12} \approx 0.57349 a^2 h</math><ref name="mw"/>

=== 詹森多面體 ===
若一個正五角錐底面和側面皆為正多邊形，則這種立體是一種[[詹森多面體|詹森多面體]]（J<sub>2</sub>）中的一個。它能被看作為[[截角二十面體|截角二十面體]]被截下的其中一塊，或說是[[正二十面體|正二十面體]]被截成[[正五角锥反角柱|正五角锥反角柱]]（J<sub>11</sub>）所剩的錐體。1966年首先被{{tsl|en|Norman Johnson (mathematician)|諾曼·詹森}}命名、描述。<ref>{{citation
 | last = Johnson | first = Norman W.
 | doi = 10.4153/cjm-1966-021-8
 | journal = Canadian Journal of Mathematics
 | mr = 0185507
 | pages = 169–200
 | title = Convex polyhedra with regular faces
 | volume = 18
 | year = 1966
 | zbl = 0132.14603 }}.</ref>

若一正五角錐的底面和側面都是正多邊形，則其高可透過邊長決定：
:<math>H = \left(\sqrt{{\frac{5-\sqrt{5}}{10}}}\right)a \approx 0.52573a.</math><ref name="pye" />

正五角錐的[[表面積|表面積]]<math>A</math>與[[體積|體積]]<math>V</math>為：
:<math>A = \frac{a^2}{2}\sqrt{\frac{5}{2}\left(10+\sqrt{5}+\sqrt{75+30\sqrt{5}}\right)} \approx 3.88554 \cdot a^2.</math><ref name="mw">{{Cite mathworld|urlname=PentagonalPyramid|title=Pentagonal Pyramid|access-date=2020-04-12}}</ref><ref name="pye">{{cite journal |last=Sapiña |first=R. |title=Area and volume of a pentagonal pyramid and Johnson solid J₂ |url=https://www.problemasyecuaciones.com/geometria3D/volumen/Johnson/J2/calculadora-area-volumen-formulas.html |issn=2659-9899 |access-date=2020-06-29 |language=es |journal=Problemas y ecuaciones |archive-date=2021-11-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211113143054/https://www.problemasyecuaciones.com/geometria3D/volumen/Johnson/J2/calculadora-area-volumen-formulas.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>
:<math>V = \left(\frac{5 + \sqrt{5}}{24}\right)a^3 \approx 0.30150a^3.</math><ref name="mw" />

== 五角星錐 ==
